title: PENTAKILL JINX!!!

embed.description: SUBSCRIBE AND LET'S PLAY TOGETHER!!! :D SHARE AND LIKE TO SPREAD THE WORD!!! :D ======================================================= FOLLOW ON TWITTER: https://twitter.com/642Games

body:
**Hey!**

I'm trying to start a new channel on YouTube which would feature tons of gameplays from me and from others who are willing to share. Anything goes!
Still, let me share with **You** guys this video where a player called Hello Im Andy makes a **PENTAKILL** in about 5 seconds :D
If you have some free time, please check out my channel, leave a comment there regarding what should I do better in **Your** opinion because I don't have much experience in using YouTube yet, however I'm willing to learn! :)

**Thanks and have a nice day everyone!!! :)**

replies.body:
Nice. :)

You should post this on the [international (english) boards](http://boards.eune.leagueoflegends.com/en/), more people will see it there. This forum is mainly for Hungarians, and some of us can't even speak english..

Good luck with your YT channel! ;)
Okay, I will, thanks or as you say: Koszonom! :)

This is the hungarian boards and no one cares.

http://media.tumblr.com/tumblr_m4tsramCAy1qzyang.gif
Hát igen... Aztán majd mondják, hogy de bunkók a magyarok. :S Pont az ilyenek miatt...
De ne a magyar fórumon hirdessen már. Senkit sem érdekel, hogy mit csinált egy videóban.
Honnan tudod, hogy senkit sem? Én például szeretem nézni az ilyen videós összeállításokat.
Miért a magyar fórumra írod ki?
